Subtask 2.8: Advanced UFW Configuration
Create a custom application profile. First, create a profile file:

sudo nano /etc/ufw/applications.d/myapp
Add the following content:

[MyWebApp]
title=My Custom Web Application
description=Custom web application running on port 8080
ports=8080/tcp
Update the application list and allow the custom application:

sudo ufw app update MyWebApp
sudo ufw allow MyWebApp
